Job Description
Dawn Bread a renowned brand in FMCG is looking for following:
1- Production in-charge: (Lahore)
- Qualification: Graduate/ Diploma Holder.
- Experience: Min 5 years experience in FMCG production.
- Age not less than 30 years.
2- Deputy Manager Accounts: (Gujranwala)
- Qualification: MBA Hnance/ACCA/ACMA
- Experience: Minimum 6	years of Account/Management experience.
- Proven Deputy Account Management skills required in order to create, maintain and enhance relationships.
The candidate should have:
- Technical competence (understand software, hardware, networks, etc).
- Extremely detail oriented.
- Motivated, goal oriented, persistent and a skilled negotiator.
- Capable enough to take initiative & create conductive environment.
- Excellent written and verbal communication skills.
- Hand stressful situations and meet deadlines.
- Plans formulations and carrying out responsibilities with minimal direction.
- The candidate should be resident of Gujranwala or near areas.Apply Instructions for This Job
Send your resume latest by 10-05-14 at:
39-Quaide Azam Industrial Estate, Kot Lakhpat Lahore.
